---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Experience | Jakob Figur"
  description="Professional experience in AI engineering, technical consulting, and system architecture."
>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Professional Experience</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; max-width: 800px; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
      A timeline of my journey in AI engineering, technical consulting, and system architecture.
      Each role has shaped my understanding of how to bridge cutting-edge technology with
      real-world business impact.
    </p>

    <div style="margin-top: 3rem;">
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
        <div class="timeline-period">2023 - Present</div>
        <h3 class="timeline-title">Technical Consultant</h3>
        <div class="timeline-company">Digistore24</div>
        <p class="timeline-description">
          Leading AI strategy and implementation across the organization. Architecting intelligent
          systems that enhance platform capabilities, optimize operations, and create new revenue
          streams. Driving technical transformation initiatives that modernize infrastructure
          and establish best practices.
        </p>
        <div class="timeline-impact">
          <strong>Impact:</strong> Spearheaded adoption of AI-powered features, established
          MLOps practices, and built internal AI capabilities enabling the team to iterate
          independently on intelligent features.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
        <div class="timeline-period">2021 - 2023</div>
        <h3 class="timeline-title">AI Systems Engineer</h3>
        <div class="timeline-company">Various Consulting Projects</div>
        <p class="timeline-description">
          Designed and deployed production AI systems for clients across industries. Specialized
          in natural language processing, computer vision, and recommendation systems. Focused
          on building scalable architectures that handle real-world complexity while maintaining
          performance and reliability.
        </p>
        <div class="timeline-impact">
          <strong>Key Projects:</strong> Developed custom NLP pipelines for document processing,
          built real-time recommendation engines, and implemented computer vision systems for
          quality control automation.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
        <div class="timeline-period">2019 - 2021</div>
        <h3 class="timeline-title">Research Assistant</h3>
        <div class="timeline-company">Academic Research</div>
        <p class="timeline-description">
          Conducted research in machine learning and artificial intelligence, focusing on
          practical applications of deep learning techniques. Published papers on novel
          architectures and contributed to open-source ML frameworks. Developed strong
          foundations in mathematical theory and experimental methodology.
        </p>
        <div class="timeline-impact">
          <strong>Contributions:</strong> Published research on neural architecture optimization,
          contributed to TensorFlow ecosystem, and mentored junior researchers on best practices
          in ML experimentation.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Technical Proficiency Section -->
    <div style="margin-top: 5rem;">
      <h2>Technical Proficiency</h2>
      <div class="grid-2" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">AI & Machine Learning</h3>
          <p>
            Deep Learning (PyTorch, TensorFlow), NLP (Transformers, LLMs), Computer Vision,
            Reinforcement Learning, MLOps (MLflow, Weights & Biases), Model Deployment
            (TorchServe, ONNX)
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Software Engineering</h3>
          <p>
            Python (Expert), TypeScript/JavaScript, Go, System Design, Microservices Architecture,
            API Design (REST, GraphQL), Testing & CI/CD, Performance Optimization
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Infrastructure & DevOps</h3>
          <p>
            Docker, Kubernetes, AWS/GCP, Terraform, GitHub Actions, Monitoring & Observability
            (Prometheus, Grafana), Database Design (PostgreSQL, Redis, Vector DBs)
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Leadership & Strategy</h3>
          <p>
            Technical Roadmapping, Cross-functional Communication, Stakeholder Management,
            Team Mentoring, Agile Methodologies, Technology Evaluation & Selection
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
